QuestData.Title: Servants of a Dead God
QuestData.Description: Even in death, Sethe exerts influence. The Sethekk cult was born of this influence: led by a false king in service of the dead god.$B$BSilence their prophets, for they seek a future of black seas and blighted skies.$B$BDefeat their chosen champions, for they have pledged themselves to a lie.
QuestData.LogDescription: Slay $1oa Sethekk Prophets and $2oa Sethekk Chosen in Sethekk Hollow.
QuestData.RewardText: Weapons and zealotry do not make one strong.$B$BThey turned to Sethe because they were too weak to face death.
